quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,"Uye avo vasingatendi vanoti: “Kana tave huruva isu nemadzibaba edu, zvirokwazvo tichaunzwa (zvakare) here?”"
  27,68,"“Zvirokwazvo takavimbiswa izvi isu nemadzitateguru edu mushure (medu), zvirokwazvo, hapana zviripo kunze kwengano dzekare.”"
  27,69,"Taura (Muhammad (SAW)) kwavari: “Fambai munyika uye muone akave magumo evairamba (vatadzi).”"
  27,70,"Usava unoshungurudzika pamusoro pavo, kana kutsutsumwa nemhaka yezvavanoronga"
  27,71,"Uye avo (vasingatendi) vanoti: “Ndirinhi (apo) vimbiso iyi (ichazadziswa), kana muri pachokwadi?”"
  27,72,"Taura: “Dzimwe dzenguva zvamunoshuvira kuti zvikasike zviri pedyo mumashure menyu.”"
  27,73,"“Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vakazara netsitsi kuvanhu, asi vakawanda vavo havatendi.”"
  27,74,"Uye zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vanoziva zvakahwanda zviri muhana dzavo uye zvavanoburitsa"
  27,75,"Uye hapana chakavanzika mumatenga uye nepasi, asi kuti zviri muGwaro rakajeka (Al-Lauh Al- Mahfoodh)"
  27,76,"Zvirokwazvo, Qur’an iri rinotaura kuvana veIzrairi izvo zvakawanda zvavanosiyana"
  27,77,"Uye zvirokwazvo, inhungamiri (Qur’aan iri) uye netsitsi kuvatendi"
  27,78,"Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vachatonga pakati pavo nemutongo wavo. Uye ndivo mukuru, muzivi wezvose"
  27,79,"Saka isa vimbo yako kuna Allah; zvirokwazvo, uri (Muhammad (SAW)) pachokwadi chiri pachena"
  27,80,"Zvirokwazvo, haungaite kuti vafi vanzwe kana kuti vanamatsi vanzwe kushevedza, apo pavanotiza, vachipira misana yavo"
  27,81,"Kana kutungamira mapofu kubva mukurasika. Unongokwanisa kuti vanzwe avo vanotenda muzvidzidziso zvedu, uye neavo vakazvipira (maMuslim)"
  27,82,"Uye kana shoko (redambudzo) razadziswa kwavari, tichaunza kubva pasi mhuka kwavari, ichitaura navo nemhosva yokuti vanhu havatendi muhuchokwadi hwendima dzedu"